<TEI xmlns="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" xmlns:frus="http://history.state.gov/frus/ns/1.0"><text><body><div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1917-11-04T04:30:00-05:00" frus:doc-dateTime-min="1917-11-03T17:00:00-05:00" n="304" subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d304">
                            <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 861.77/208</note>
                            <head><hi rend="italic">The Chairman of the Advisory Commission of
                                    Railway Experts to Russia</hi> (<persName corresp="#p_SJF1" type="from"><hi rend="italic">Stevens</hi></persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                                    State</gloss></hi></head>
                            <opener>
                                <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram]</seg>
                            </opener>
                            <opener>
                                <dateline rendition="#right"><placeName><hi rend="smallcaps">Petrograd</hi></placeName>, <date ana="#date_undated-inferred-from-document-content-and-sibling-dates" calendar="gregorian" notAfter="1917-11-04T04:30:00-05:00" notBefore="1917-11-03T17:00:00-05:00"><hi rend="italic">undated</hi></date>. <lb/> [<hi rend="italic">Received
                                        November 4, 1917, 4.30 a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                            </opener>
                            <p>For <persName corresp="#p_WD1">Willard</persName>:</p>
                            <p>I am leaving Petrograd to try to improve operation of lines Omsk to
                                Moscow to handle vast amount of food Siberia to Central Russia.
                                Russian Government claims this is the most important problem in
                                Russia and absolutely vital to existence. Can you send eight more
                                    <pb facs="0255" n="205" xml:id="pg_205"/> units if I find
                                necessary? Have gratifying reports from Siberian line.</p>
                            <closer>
                                <signed><persName corresp="#p_SJF1"><hi rend="smallcaps">Stevens</hi></persName></signed>
                            </closer>
                        </div>
                        </body></text></TEI>